after it

*Zabrinuta* je čekala na njegov odgovor. (She was worried while she waited for his answer.)

Ona je bila *zabrinuta* zbog njegovog ponašanja. (She was concerned about his behavior.)

Njegova majka je bila *zabrinuta* za njega. (His mother was worried about him.)

Nastavnica je bila *zabrinuta* zbog njegovih rezultata. (The teacher was worried about his results.)

Klinci su bili *zabrinuti* za budućnost. (The kids were worried about the future.)